Package com.opengamma.strata.pricer.impl.volatility.smile

Class SabrFormulaData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.opengamma.strata.pricer.impl.volatility.smile.SabrFormulaData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SmileModelData, java.io.Serializable, org.joda.beans.Bean, org.joda.beans.ImmutableBean
    public final class SabrFormulaData
extends java.lang.Object
implements SmileModelData, org.joda.beans.ImmutableBean, java.io.Serializable
    The data bundle for SABR formula.

    The bundle contains the SABR model parameters, alpha, beta, rho and nu, as an array.

      • getParameters

        public DoubleArray getParameters()
        Gets the model parameters.

        This must be an array of length 4. The parameters in the array are in the order of alpha, beta, rho and nu. The constraints for the parameters are defined in isAllowed(int, double).

        Returns:
        the value of the property, not null
